data.description: Welcome to 2216 Afton. This home currently has 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 2 separate kitchens. The basement is newly renovated and has outdoor access.  Large fenced backyard and detached one car garage back right up to a one-way alley allowing for plenty of off-street parking This home could easily be converted back into a duplex: Main and basement 3 bed 2 bath with potential rental  income of $2,000/mo. And the upstairs is 2 bed 1 bath for a  potential $1,800/mo. The home already has separate gas meters and electric panels. The potential is endless. Schedule your appointment today.
